<div class="span4">
<h2>Colophon</h2>
<p>
This page feeds the
<a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AjxnOozsvYvldHY1NE1MV0pGVXRyd2hUaTAzdmRJb1E">Timeline of Open Source in Government Spreadsheet</a> 
and 
<a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=1-z0AiiGbiW8aCcXjupeHVoH_g5LadO2K2dmyIIPuaRY">Government Released Open Source Software</a> 
into a <a href="http://simile.mit.edu/timeline/">Simile Timeline widget</a>. 
It is based on the work of <a href="http://kiyo.wordpress.com/2007/04/29/google-spreadsheet-json-to-timeline/">Kiyohito Yamamoto</a>.
You can find the source for this at <a href="https://github.com/OpenTechStrategies/us-govt-open-source">GitHub</a>
</p>
